text.tspan: FBApp is a utility class to provide
the centeral place for window & messaging management.
When want to cut the dependencies from the external libaries. For example
fastbird engine cut the dependency to the OpenColladaLibrary by introducing
the DLL FBColladaImporter. This also guarantees faster link time and better
tolerance to the future changes on the external libraries.
Feature is small and can be reusable for building other APIs or applications.
